About this item

  • Commercial Kitchen Sink Faucet – This 36" height wall-mounted pre-rinse faucet with sprayer and add-on faucet ultra-high pressure (1.42GPM) for extreme cleaning power. Ideal for efficient and excellent cleaning of excess food and sauces from plates.
  • High Quality Commercial Sink Faucet: Commercial Sink Faucet have a polished chrome-plated surface with excellent rust resistance, and their interiors are made of lead-free brass for durability, which is also designed with a double-layer leak-proof structure to ensure that no water leaks when in use.
  • 8 Inches Adjustable Center Wall Mount Faucet – This commercial kitchen faucet mounts to the wall using a pair of G1/2" female inlets. Those inlets can adjust from 7 3/4" to 8 1/4". Allowing you to fit them directly onto your facility's water lines with ease. Suitable for 1, 2 or 3 compartment professional grade commercial kitchen sink use.
  • Commercial Faucet With Pre-Rinse Shower - 38" flexible stainless steel hose with pre-rinse shower and 12" swivel spout that swivels 360 degrees, 90° swivel double handles control hot and cold water for easy use and water changes.
  • After-Sales Service That Makes You Satisfied: All commercial kitchen faucets come with a 90-day return and money back guarantee. If you have any questions, please feel free to contact us.

Product Description

38" flexible stainless steel hose

Stainless steel pre-rinse hose inner tube is made of non-toxic, odourless EPDM material and and is resistant to high pressure.

The spring is made of 304 stainless steel

The spring is strong and stable and helps maintain the shape of the hose and position the spray valve over the sink.

High Quality Aerator

Provides you with a soft washing experience and avoids splashing.

Commercial Sink Faucet have a polished chrome-plated surface with excellent rust resistance, and their interiors are made of lead-free brass for durability, which is also designed with a double-layer leak-proof structure to ensure that no water leaks when in use.

How customer reviews and ratings work

Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

5 out of 5 stars
Easy to install and use
This 21-inch high commercial faucet is very practical, with a sprayer and swinging outlet to meet a variety of needs. The faucet's 8-inch adjustable center and 8-inch additional swinging outlet are flexible, and both rotary and sprayer operation are smooth, suitable for wall-mounted kitchen sinks, and easy and quick to install. The material is durable and the surface is smooth and easy to clean. The sprayer's strong water pressure makes it ideal for rinsing utensils and cleaning sinks. The swinging water outlet can easily adjust the direction, convenient for use in different areas, very practical.

It’s going to be a centerpiece of my dream Mediterranean kitchen with the half-moon island when we finish rehabbing our (soon to be beautiful) old house, which my kids, not-so-lovingly, call "the Bando" but I oh-so-lovingly refer to it as the "Alhambra" because I can already see the soul of this place shining through.

About this Item

  • Commercial Kitchen Sink Faucet – This 36" height wall-mounted pre-rinse faucet with sprayer and add-on faucet ultra-high pressure (1.42GPM) for extreme cleaning power. Ideal for efficient and excellent cleaning of excess food and sauces from plates.
  • High Quality Commercial Sink Faucet: Commercial Sink Faucet have a polished chrome-plated surface with excellent rust resistance, and their interiors are made of lead-free brass for durability, which is also designed with a double-layer leak-proof structure to ensure that no water leaks when in use.
  • 8 Inches Adjustable Center Wall Mount Faucet – This commercial kitchen faucet mounts to the wall using a pair of G1/2" female inlets. Those inlets can adjust from 7 3/4" to 8 1/4". Allowing you to fit them directly onto your facility's water lines with ease. Suitable for 1, 2 or 3 compartment professional grade commercial kitchen sink use.
